An '''adventure''' is an exciting experience that is typically a bold, sometimes [[risk]]y, undertaking.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/adventure |title=Adventure |work=dictionary.com |date= |accessdate=2013-06-13}}</ref> Adventures may be activities with some potential for physical danger such as [[traveling]], [[exploring]], [[skydiving]], [[mountain climbing]], [[scuba diving]], [[river rafting]] or participating in [[extreme sports]]. Adventures are often undertaken to create psychological [[arousal]] or in order to achieve a greater goal such as the pursuit of knowledge that can only be obtained in a risky manner.
